&lt;p&gt;This post is Fixed term for 18 months&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a part time Medical Workforce Assistant to join our team based in Glangwili Hospital, Carmarthen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role involves working in a busy office environment and you will need to be organised and efficient as well as being able to work well under pressure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have excellent communication skills with proven recent administration experience including keyboard skills and the use of Microsoft word, excel and database systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates will also need to demonstrate a high degree of attention to detail and have the ability to prioritise their workload in order to meet tight timescales that need to be followed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held on 18.11.20.&lt;/p&gt;
